      <item>
        <title>Iniciar Vagrant no Windows com bat</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Iniciar a VM do vagrant através de um arquivo &lt;code&gt;.bat&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;highlight&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;language-bat&quot; data-lang=&quot;bat&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;@&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;off&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;cd&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;/d&lt;/span&gt; \path\dir\vagrant

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;n&quot;&gt;/f&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;tokens=2 delims= &amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;%%a&lt;/span&gt; in (&lt;span class=&quot;s1&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;vagrant status ^| find /i &amp;quot;default&amp;quot;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;do&lt;/span&gt; (
  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;SET&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;STATE&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;%%a&lt;/span&gt;
)

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;%STATE%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;equ&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;running&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; (
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;  @&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; Vagrant VM is running...
) &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; (
  &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;nv&quot;&gt;%STATE%&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;o&quot;&gt;equ&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;s2&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;saved&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt; (
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;    @&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; Starting Vagrant VM from powered down state...
    vagrant up
  ) &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; (
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;    @&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; Resuming Vagrant VM from saved state...
    vagrant resume
  )
)

&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;errorlevel&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;m&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt; (
&lt;span class=&quot;p&quot;&gt;  @&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;k&quot;&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; FAILURE! Vagrant VM unresponsive...
)&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</description>
        <pubDate>Sun, 31 Jan 2016 19:57:00 -0200</pubDate>
